title: #92Noon Vox in the Box! Boudreau/Winnik/Russo/Ramsey/Florio/Mileski
description: The Wild take on the Jets in Game 4 tonight and PA is live from the battleground! Joining PA inside the Xcel Energy Center penalty box is The FAN's Brandon Mileski, Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau, Wild Forward Daniel Winnik, The Athletic's Michael Russo, and K102's Rachel Ramsey! Also, ProFootballTalk's Mike Florio makes his regular appearance on #92Noon!
